{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">ABOUT THIS GAME</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Brawl with fists, swords, bows, and even boomerangs!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\ud83d\udd25 Blaze through the battlefield using your Gauntlets \ud83d\udd25</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2511050/extras/75203624_894001768826699_6790289070927780263_n.gif?t=1738746841\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Brazen Blaze is a high-speed VR multiplayer action game. Use your Gauntlets to smash through enemies and buildings! Master your 360\u00b0 Boost Dash to soar through the skies as you aim to become the world\u2019s strongest Runner!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\ud83d\udc4a Smash your enemies by any means necessary \ud83d\udc4a</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2511050/extras/38974748_886521986333997_1027583894120253985_n.gif?t=1738746841\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Not only do you have your character's unique Gauntlet and weapons at your disposal, but also random items that appear on the battlefield to help take down your foes. Rocket launchers, illegal bats, beam sabers, and\u2026 energy drinks?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\ud83d\ude80 Destroy the stage \ud83d\ude80</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2511050/extras/75395599_1252104769161374_5913382075458269030_n.gif?t=1738746841\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every building on the stage is destructible, allowing you to create your own battlefield advantage! But be warned! Buildings crumble during the fight, and stages fall apart over time, changing the course of the battle.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2511050/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738746841","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_ite